1
00:00:00,521 --> 00:00:08,621
<i>Yeah, turn your sadness into kindness,</i>
<i>your uniqueness into strength</i>

2
00:00:08,796 --> 00:00:17,033
<i>Even if you get lost, let's start walking</i>

3
00:00:17,271 --> 00:00:19,262
<i>One more time</i>

4
00:00:22,276 --> 00:00:26,042
<i>Are you really happy</i>

5
00:00:26,113 --> 00:00:29,480
<i>when you're always meeting</i>
<i>to someone's expectations?</i>

6
00:00:29,683 --> 00:00:33,244
<i>Even if you change to</i>
<i>who you really wanna be</i>

7
00:00:33,621 --> 00:00:36,988
<i>Will you always have a great smile?</i>

8
00:00:37,058 --> 00:00:44,487
<i>Dreaming of only "the beginning,"</i>
<i>I wake up</i>

9
00:00:44,565 --> 00:00:53,701
<i>and someday, I'll live on my own.</i>

10
00:00:53,774 --> 00:01:01,806
<i>Yes, precious things are never in shape</i>

11
00:01:02,049 --> 00:01:08,887
<i>You never know what it is</i>
<i>when you get it or lose it</i>

12
00:01:08,956 --> 00:01:17,022
<i>Yeah, turn your sadness into kindness,</i>
<i>your uniqueness into strength</i>

13
00:01:17,331 --> 00:01:25,796
<i>Even if you get lost,</i>
<i>let's start walking</i>

14
00:01:25,873 --> 00:01:27,898
<i>One more time</i>

15
00:01:41,400 --> 00:01:42,389
Dang it!

16
00:01:50,308 --> 00:01:53,937
<i>Darn it! Things will really be bad</i>
<i>if it stays like this...!</i>

17
00:01:57,716 --> 00:01:58,614
<i>I'll have to...</i>

18
00:02:01,520 --> 00:02:05,149
I'll have to save...
everyone for sure!

19
00:02:06,291 --> 00:02:12,161
<i>Light vs. Dark.</i>
<i>The Two Faces of Gaara!</i>

20
00:02:24,142 --> 00:02:26,770
So you'll fight for the sake of others?!

21
00:02:28,613 --> 00:02:30,911
That's why you guys are
only at that level!

22
00:02:31,383 --> 00:02:33,578
You don't need a reason to fight!

23
00:02:35,520 --> 00:02:39,251
Only the one who remains undefeated
can actually feel his own existence!

24
00:02:39,891 --> 00:02:42,985
Come on, forget about
your insignificant friends

25
00:02:43,061 --> 00:02:45,586
and fight only for the sake
of your own existence!

26
00:02:46,398 --> 00:02:47,387
Insignificant...

27
00:02:49,301 --> 00:02:50,461
friends?

28
00:02:53,205 --> 00:02:57,039
Those who hold silly sentiments
about fighting

29
00:02:57,342 --> 00:02:58,400
should just die!

30
00:02:58,710 --> 00:03:00,940
I'm sick of listening to you talk!

31
00:03:01,913 --> 00:03:03,813
I'll clobber you for sure!

32
00:03:07,452 --> 00:03:10,387
You guys misunderstand real strength!

33
00:03:11,356 --> 00:03:12,687
Shut up!

34
00:04:04,509 --> 00:04:06,909
W-Why...? Why is it?!

35
00:04:07,646 --> 00:04:09,580
Why Yashamaru...?

36
00:04:10,315 --> 00:04:12,215
Why did you, why...?

37
00:04:15,954 --> 00:04:17,387
Why...?

38
00:04:18,290 --> 00:04:19,552
<i>Love is...</i>

39
00:04:19,624 --> 00:04:22,957
<i>a heart that desires to serve</i>
<i>a precious person who is close to oneself,</i>

40
00:04:23,228 --> 00:04:25,492
<i>to love and watch over that person.</i>

41
00:04:26,131 --> 00:04:27,428
<i>Just like my older sister did.</i>

42
00:04:30,835 --> 00:04:34,794
<i>You are a precious person</i>
<i>who is close to me, Gaara!</i>

43
00:04:36,975 --> 00:04:42,208
Always...
only Yashamaru would always...

44
00:04:42,547 --> 00:04:44,174
Me... always me...

45
00:04:46,885 --> 00:04:47,943
It was an order.

46
00:04:50,722 --> 00:04:54,158
I was commissioned to kill you...

47
00:04:57,529 --> 00:04:58,928
By your father...

48
00:05:00,432 --> 00:05:01,456
Lord Kazekage

49
00:05:05,203 --> 00:05:06,329
My father...?

50
00:05:15,013 --> 00:05:17,140
Why did my father...?

51
00:05:17,449 --> 00:05:18,711
Why...? Why me?

52
00:05:20,452 --> 00:05:23,979
Gaara, you who were born and possessed
by the Sand Spirit Shukaku...

53
00:05:24,823 --> 00:05:28,623
have been watched over
as an experiment.

54
00:05:31,162 --> 00:05:35,258
However, Gaara, you couldn't
control the living spirit Shukaku,

55
00:05:35,333 --> 00:05:38,996
the Sand Spirit which possesses
the power of the sand.

56
00:05:40,005 --> 00:05:44,203
Eventually your existence would
become too dangerous for the village.

57
00:05:46,745 --> 00:05:48,178
Before that occurred...

58
00:05:51,283 --> 00:05:53,581
So Yashamaru, you had not choice...

59
00:05:54,119 --> 00:05:55,882
but to comply with my father's order...?

60
00:05:57,689 --> 00:06:00,180
No... That is not correct.

61
00:06:02,594 --> 00:06:05,358
It is true I accepted
Lord Kazekage's order.

62
00:06:06,364 --> 00:06:10,198
But if I had wanted to turn it down,
I could have turned it down.

63
00:06:13,405 --> 00:06:14,372
Gaara...

64
00:06:15,774 --> 00:06:20,040
Deep down in my heart,
I probably...

65
00:06:21,780 --> 00:06:22,906
hated you.

66
00:06:24,416 --> 00:06:27,180
You, whose birth took the life
of my beloved older sister.

67
00:06:27,852 --> 00:06:29,945
The child she left behind in death...

68
00:06:30,889 --> 00:06:37,385
Thinking that you were her remembrance,
I tried desperately to love you.

69
00:06:38,263 --> 00:06:40,754
However... I was not able to.

70
00:06:41,933 --> 00:06:45,061
My sister didn't choose to have you.

71
00:06:46,171 --> 00:06:48,435
My sister became a sacrifice
for the village,

72
00:06:48,707 --> 00:06:51,039
and she died while
cursing this village!

73
00:06:52,911 --> 00:06:54,606
From that time, I probably...

74
00:06:55,013 --> 00:06:58,710
have been burdened with a wound
of the heart that could never heal.

75
00:06:59,751 --> 00:07:03,016
<i>Unlike a wound on the body,</i>
<i>there is no ointment and sometimes,</i>

76
00:07:03,088 --> 00:07:05,318
<i>it doesn't heal for one's entire life.</i>

77
00:07:07,192 --> 00:07:08,625
<i>A wound of the heart?</i>

78
00:07:12,464 --> 00:07:15,865
Your name...
is the name my sister gave you.

79
00:07:19,003 --> 00:07:21,096
"This child's name is Gaara...

80
00:07:21,840 --> 00:07:23,569
"A devil that loves only itself...

81
00:07:24,008 --> 00:07:25,771
"Love only yourself...

82
00:07:26,745 --> 00:07:29,714
"And fight only for
your own sake.

83
00:07:30,882 --> 00:07:33,612
"If you do that,
you will continue to exist."

84
00:07:34,052 --> 00:07:36,145
Such was the hope it contained.

85
00:07:36,755 --> 00:07:37,619
However...

86
00:07:37,989 --> 00:07:40,219
my sister did not give you this name

87
00:07:40,291 --> 00:07:43,021
because she was concerned
about you or loved you.

88
00:07:43,361 --> 00:07:47,661
The reason she gave you this name,
a name so you would continue to exist...

89
00:07:50,101 --> 00:07:52,296
...was so that the deep seated hatred
of my sister

90
00:07:52,370 --> 00:07:55,305
who died hating and cursing
this village...

91
00:07:57,108 --> 00:07:59,167
would remain...

92
00:08:01,746 --> 00:08:03,543
and be known to all!

93
00:08:20,265 --> 00:08:24,258
You were never... loved!

94
00:08:33,611 --> 00:08:34,407
This is the last...

95
00:08:36,581 --> 00:08:37,707
Please die...

96
00:09:07,512 --> 00:09:11,448
<i>I believe that my sister loved you, Gaara.</i>

97
00:09:12,550 --> 00:09:13,608
<i>Love?</i>

98
00:09:20,525 --> 00:09:25,553
<i>The sand automatically trying to</i>
<i>protect you is like the love of a mother.</i>

99
00:09:26,130 --> 00:09:30,829
<i>I believe that sand is filled</i>
<i>with your mother's will.</i>

100
00:09:38,243 --> 00:09:39,335
<i>Love.</i>

101
00:10:26,324 --> 00:10:28,519
<i>Love only yourself.</i>

102
00:10:28,993 --> 00:10:32,622
<i>And fight only for your own sake.</i>

103
00:10:33,798 --> 00:10:36,528
So that is Gaara...
That is me.

104
00:10:37,235 --> 00:10:38,759
I finally understand.

105
00:10:40,872 --> 00:10:42,203
I am alone.

106
00:10:43,107 --> 00:10:46,270
I will no longer believe in anyone...
or love anyone.

107
00:10:47,979 --> 00:10:49,276
I am alone!

108
00:10:54,519 --> 00:10:57,386
Yes, I am all by myself.

109
00:11:13,871 --> 00:11:16,465
What's the matter?
Hurry up and come at me!

110
00:11:16,874 --> 00:11:20,332
Don't you care what happens
to your so-called precious friends?!

111
00:11:22,814 --> 00:11:23,508
Sakura!

112
00:11:27,785 --> 00:11:28,752
Dang it!

113
00:11:30,088 --> 00:11:31,783
<i>Naruto's not his usual self...</i>

114
00:11:32,724 --> 00:11:35,124
<i>Did something happen between them?</i>

115
00:11:36,160 --> 00:11:37,149
<i>In any case...</i>

116
00:11:37,562 --> 00:11:39,962
<i>In any case,</i>
<i>I need to save Sakura!</i>

117
00:11:41,065 --> 00:11:43,226
<i>But... what to do?!</i>

118
00:11:45,470 --> 00:11:46,698
<i>That's it!</i>

119
00:11:47,138 --> 00:11:49,732
<i>Since it's come to this...</i>
<i>Though it's gonna use up a lot of Chakra...</i>

120
00:11:51,709 --> 00:11:55,304
<i>There's no choice</i>
<i>but to summon the Chief Gamabunta!</i>

121
00:12:00,652 --> 00:12:02,142
Summoning Jutsu!

122
00:12:11,029 --> 00:12:12,656
What's this?! You're a little kid!

123
00:12:13,064 --> 00:12:15,157
If you want something from me,
give me some snack!

124
00:12:15,566 --> 00:12:17,898
If you don't, I won't play with you!

125
00:12:18,069 --> 00:12:21,527
You know something?
I hate you frogs!

126
00:12:21,606 --> 00:12:24,871
What did you say?!
Don't make fun of amphibians! Really!

127
00:12:25,743 --> 00:12:29,509
Jeez, I don't have time to
play with you, little squirt!

128
00:12:32,183 --> 00:12:34,014
<i>Darn! Why is it...?</i>

129
00:12:34,085 --> 00:12:37,748
<i>I practiced for so long, but with this,</i>
<i>there's no other way...</i>

130
00:12:38,623 --> 00:12:40,557
I need to save everyone!

131
00:12:42,026 --> 00:12:44,221
Everyone... you say?

132
00:12:44,529 --> 00:12:45,860
Don't make me laugh.

133
00:12:46,330 --> 00:12:49,265
I fight... only for myself!

134
00:12:54,605 --> 00:12:57,039
<i>He...he's transforming again!</i>

135
00:13:00,878 --> 00:13:04,678
If you don't take me down,
the sand over this girl won't fall away!

136
00:13:05,283 --> 00:13:08,446
Not only that, as time passes...

137
00:13:08,519 --> 00:13:11,920
this sand will slowly squeeze tighter
and eventually suffocate this girl!

138
00:13:13,357 --> 00:13:14,346
<i>Sakura!</i>

139
00:13:15,393 --> 00:13:17,827
<i>He's getting closer and closer</i>
<i>to being a Perfect Possession.</i>

140
00:13:18,896 --> 00:13:21,091
<i>That Jutsu hasn't been activated yet,</i>

141
00:13:21,499 --> 00:13:23,228
<i>but at this rate, I'll also be...!</i>

142
00:13:28,139 --> 00:13:29,037
<i>Those eyes...</i>

143
00:13:30,675 --> 00:13:32,142
Sand Shuriken!

144
00:13:45,656 --> 00:13:47,351
You're... really weak!

145
00:13:48,059 --> 00:13:48,889
Shut up!

146
00:13:49,393 --> 00:13:51,020
But what is that guy?

147
00:14:09,247 --> 00:14:12,705
You're persistent...
Sarutobi Sensei!

148
00:14:16,188 --> 00:14:17,678
<i>I-It doesn't move?!</i>

149
00:14:19,658 --> 00:14:21,523
Y-You hard to kill fools!

150
00:14:24,396 --> 00:14:27,263
Do you still not understand, Orochimaru?

151
00:14:29,034 --> 00:14:31,594
The Leaf Village is my home!

152
00:14:32,070 --> 00:14:35,699
I told you I am the pillar
of that house!

153
00:14:36,308 --> 00:14:41,302
That's why I'm saying
I will break that pillar!

154
00:14:41,480 --> 00:14:43,345
As long as the people of the village

155
00:14:43,415 --> 00:14:47,818
fiercely fight to protect
their dear comrades,

156
00:14:47,886 --> 00:14:51,686
the pillar of the Leaf Village will not
be broken by the likes of you!

157
00:14:52,090 --> 00:14:53,990
I wonder about that.

158
00:14:55,394 --> 00:14:57,453
Do not underestimate the Hokage!

159
00:15:00,732 --> 00:15:01,699
I-Impossible...!

160
00:15:02,300 --> 00:15:06,566
Where is...?
Most of your Chakra should be gone!

161
00:15:06,972 --> 00:15:11,966
Chakra and Ninjutsu are
not all there is to strength!

162
00:15:15,981 --> 00:15:18,040
<i>W-What lonely eyes...</i>

163
00:15:19,317 --> 00:15:21,785
<i>Such lonely eyes...</i>

164
00:15:24,122 --> 00:15:28,821
<i>This guy is also turning into a monster...</i>
<i>the same as me.</i>

165
00:15:38,136 --> 00:15:40,434
<i>I hated every last one of them.</i>

166
00:15:41,273 --> 00:15:42,865
<i>I didn't understand who I was,</i>

167
00:15:43,008 --> 00:15:47,672
<i>why I was so hated,</i>
<i>why I even existed.</i>

168
00:15:48,447 --> 00:15:49,709
<i>In other words,</i>

169
00:15:50,248 --> 00:15:55,049
<i>you're the Nine Tailed Fox who killed</i>
<i>Iruka's parents and ruined the village!</i>

170
00:15:56,054 --> 00:15:59,285
<i>You've been deceived by everyone</i>
<i>in the village all along!</i>

171
00:16:00,092 --> 00:16:01,024
<i>I...</i>

172
00:16:01,426 --> 00:16:03,986
<i>When I learned that the</i>
<i>Nine Tailed Fox was inside me,</i>

173
00:16:04,396 --> 00:16:06,990
<i>everyone in the village seemed</i>
<i>even more cold hearted...</i>

174
00:16:07,866 --> 00:16:10,664
<i>I was so deeply troubled...</i>

175
00:16:13,138 --> 00:16:13,866
<i>But...</i>

176
00:16:16,708 --> 00:16:19,643
Naruto! Let's go have
ramen for a change!

177
00:16:19,945 --> 00:16:22,106
Yay! I will, I will!

178
00:16:22,414 --> 00:16:24,382
I'll have the one with
extra BBQ pork slices!

179
00:16:25,117 --> 00:16:29,076
Huh! You loser...
If you want to beat me train harder!

180
00:16:29,287 --> 00:16:32,279
Shut up! I won't lose to you!

181
00:16:32,924 --> 00:16:36,325
Hey Naruto!
What did Sasuke say about me?

182
00:16:36,628 --> 00:16:37,959
He didn't say anything...

183
00:16:38,663 --> 00:16:42,292
By the way! By the way!
Wouldn't you rather know how I feel...?

184
00:16:42,367 --> 00:16:44,392
Oh! Really, Sakura!

185
00:16:46,104 --> 00:16:47,731
I'm gonna eat now!

186
00:16:48,573 --> 00:16:53,135
Um... Naruto, you'll really die if you eat
only noodles and sweet red bean porridge.

187
00:16:53,645 --> 00:16:56,011
You're a Ninja,
so eat more vegetables!

188
00:16:56,314 --> 00:16:57,542
Here, have some!

189
00:16:57,616 --> 00:17:00,414
What?! I don't like vegetables!

190
00:17:01,720 --> 00:17:04,587
<i>People appeared</i>
<i>who acknowledged me...</i>

191
00:17:04,956 --> 00:17:06,423
<i>That's why I became all right,</i>

192
00:17:06,992 --> 00:17:09,426
<i>even though there was</i>
<i>the demon fox inside my body,</i>

193
00:17:09,494 --> 00:17:12,861
<i>or even if the people of the village</i>
<i>looked at me with cold eyes.</i>

194
00:17:13,565 --> 00:17:16,693
<i>Because...</i>
<i>I wasn't alone anymore!</i>

195
00:17:18,103 --> 00:17:21,630
<i>I never imagined how happy and</i>
<i>fortunate I could feel.</i>

196
00:17:22,741 --> 00:17:24,936
<i>How really...really...</i>

197
00:17:25,777 --> 00:17:27,039
<i>great it was.</i>

198
00:17:27,612 --> 00:17:29,079
<i>How truly great it was</i>
<i>to be here.</i>

199
00:17:29,681 --> 00:17:33,708
<i>I was relieved to know</i>
<i>I am allowed to be here, to exist!</i>

200
00:17:35,854 --> 00:17:38,584
<i>That's why it scares me</i>
<i>to think about the past...</i>

201
00:17:39,090 --> 00:17:41,024
<i>That suffering is agonizing...</i>

202
00:17:42,360 --> 00:17:44,123
<i>It's a pitch black hell!</i>

203
00:17:44,930 --> 00:17:47,728
<i>Lf...I had remained that way, all alone...</i>

204
00:17:50,402 --> 00:17:52,927
<i>That's precisely why I understand!</i>

205
00:17:54,673 --> 00:17:58,632
<i>So what did I have in this life,</i>
<i>why did I keep living?</i>

206
00:17:59,911 --> 00:18:01,572
<i>This is the answer I came to...</i>

207
00:18:02,113 --> 00:18:06,607
<i>I am living in order to kill</i>
<i>human beings other than myself.</i>

208
00:18:08,220 --> 00:18:10,245
<i>I don't know what happened, but...</i>

209
00:18:11,089 --> 00:18:14,286
<i>This guy's always been</i>
<i>suffering all alone...</i>

210
00:18:14,993 --> 00:18:16,688
<i>Even now, without ever feeling relief...</i>

211
00:18:17,095 --> 00:18:20,258
<i>Only able to believe in himself...</i>

212
00:18:21,166 --> 00:18:23,691
<i>Even now, he's battling in hell...</i>

213
00:18:24,502 --> 00:18:25,434
<i>That's how it is...</i>

214
00:18:25,870 --> 00:18:29,067
<i>To him, someone like me</i>
<i>who's acknowledged by others...</i>

215
00:18:29,241 --> 00:18:33,439
<i>might seem like a weakling in</i>
<i>a world of happiness without tension...</i>

216
00:18:35,280 --> 00:18:38,010
<i>Can I really win against</i>
<i>a guy like this?</i>

217
00:18:41,052 --> 00:18:44,078
What's the matter?!
Are you afraid of me?

218
00:18:44,589 --> 00:18:48,457
To fight for the sake of oneself?
To fight for the sake of others?

219
00:18:48,927 --> 00:18:53,489
You should just love yourself,
and fight for yourself!

220
00:18:54,032 --> 00:18:57,297
That is the definition of
the strongest one!

221
00:18:58,603 --> 00:19:00,161
Now fight me!

222
00:19:00,472 --> 00:19:02,406
What happened to
the boldness you had earlier?!

223
00:19:02,874 --> 00:19:07,334
Show me your strength!
I'll throw that strength to the ground!

224
00:19:09,481 --> 00:19:14,009
Now what's the matter?!
If you don't fight me, I'll kill that girl!

225
00:19:17,022 --> 00:19:18,512
Darn it!

226
00:19:21,626 --> 00:19:23,651
Multi Shadow Clone Jutsu!

227
00:19:26,831 --> 00:19:27,923
Wind Style!

228
00:19:30,035 --> 00:19:32,970
Infinite Sandstorm Devastation!

229
00:19:39,744 --> 00:19:42,577
<i>This isn't good...</i>
<i>He really got me.</i>

230
00:19:42,947 --> 00:19:45,814
First, I'll toy with you
without killing you!

231
00:19:45,950 --> 00:19:48,680
I look forward to seeing
when and how you give up

232
00:19:48,753 --> 00:19:50,311
and abandon your friends!

233
00:19:57,929 --> 00:19:58,793
Naruto...

234
00:20:00,498 --> 00:20:02,762
<i>But...what is it?</i>

235
00:20:05,337 --> 00:20:06,565
It's far from over!

236
00:20:18,316 --> 00:20:19,476
<i>N-Naruto...</i>

237
00:20:21,252 --> 00:20:23,914
<i>What is this...this feeling?</i>

238
00:20:24,889 --> 00:20:26,254
Sand Shuriken!

239
00:20:32,897 --> 00:20:35,627
D-Dang it!

240
00:20:36,368 --> 00:20:37,858
Dang it!

241
00:20:38,403 --> 00:20:40,098
H-He's...

242
00:20:41,072 --> 00:20:45,168
<i>What is this?!</i>
<i>This feeling that's overcoming me?</i>

243
00:20:49,447 --> 00:20:50,106
<i>Naruto...!</i>

244
00:20:53,051 --> 00:20:55,884
<i>For some reason...</i>
<i>I don't want to lose to this guy...</i>

245
00:20:56,254 --> 00:20:58,051
You...

246
00:21:01,326 --> 00:21:03,191
<i>...even if I die!</i>

247
00:21:05,663 --> 00:21:15,732
<i>Everyone makes mistakes</i>
<i>It's nothing to be ashamed about</i>

248
00:21:16,173 --> 00:21:27,016
<i>Don't let this scar be for naught</i>
<i>Walk with a smile</i>

249
00:21:37,128 --> 00:21:42,760
<i>Yes, breathe in the air</i>
<i>Lift your face to the sky and jump</i>

250
00:21:42,833 --> 00:21:47,793
<i>If it rains, take a break</i>
<i>Go where the wind takes you</i>

251
00:21:48,172 --> 00:21:53,075
<i>So many regrets</i>
<i>Don't let this scar be for naught</i>

252
00:21:53,144 --> 00:21:58,275
<i>Let's go carve the badges in our chest</i>
<i>Yes, it's Show Time, life begins now.</i>

253
00:21:58,349 --> 00:22:08,520
<i>Everyone makes mistakes</i>
<i>It's nothing to be ashamed about</i>

254
00:22:08,826 --> 00:22:19,259
<i>Don't let this scar be for naught</i>
<i>Walk with a smile</i>

255
00:22:19,336 --> 00:22:29,905
<i>Transform sadness into the wind</i>
<i>and continue to forge on</i>

256
00:22:29,980 --> 00:22:35,543
<i>Forge on strong</i>

257
00:22:47,098 --> 00:22:48,395
Hear! Hear! Hear! Hear!

258
00:22:48,466 --> 00:22:50,297
If you're far away,
listen well.

259
00:22:50,367 --> 00:22:52,028
If you're closer,
then come and watch it!

260
00:22:52,136 --> 00:22:53,763
Among all the Genin in the Leaf,

261
00:22:53,838 --> 00:22:55,806
I'm the only one who's
suited to become Hokage!

262
00:22:55,873 --> 00:22:57,670
I turn the biggest pinch
into opportunity

263
00:22:57,741 --> 00:22:59,766
with Transform Jutsu, Summoning Jutsu,
and Shadow Clone Jutsu.

264
00:22:59,844 --> 00:23:01,505
I give back twice as much
when I receive a punch.

265
00:23:01,579 --> 00:23:03,376
I'm the hyperactive knucklehead Ninja!

266
00:23:03,981 --> 00:23:08,611
This is the start of the spiraling series
of Naruto's Ninja Handbook!

267
00:23:08,986 --> 00:23:12,854
Next time: "Naruto's Ninja Handbook"
